-tricky-questions",[1252,1264,1265],"JavaScript Core","Functions and How This Works",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2021\u002F01\u002F13\u002Fjavascript-core-45-function-this-tricky-questions\u002F","Z8e5o22mrwQ2fEwqHQy8baRbqoZ7c7AiSyWAxfJHcR8",{"newer":1270,"older":1274},{"url":1271,"title":1272,"date":1273},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2021\u002F01\u002F16\u002Fjavascript-core-46-functions-and-this-exercises\u002F","JavaScript Core Concepts (46): Functions and How This Works — Practice Quiz","2021-01-16 10:03:19",{"url":1275,"title":1276,"date":1277},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2021\u002F01\u002F11\u002Fjavascript-core-44-this-practice\u002F","JavaScript Core (44) — Functions and How This Works: this Practice Problems","2021-01-11 22:01:00",[1279,1284,1289],{"url":1280,"title":1281,"date":1282,"readingMinutes":1283},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2026\u002F03\u002F10\u002Fweb-crypto-api-encryption-guide\u002F","No crypto Package, No Node.js — The Web Crypto API Does It All in the Browser","2026-03-10 09:45:08","9",{"url":1285,"title":1286,"date":1287,"readingMinutes":1288},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F08\u002Fjquery-why-it-declined\u002F","jQuery Was Once King — So Why Did It Fall Off?","2025-12-08 21:35:24","7",{"url":1290,"title":1291,"date":1292,"readingMinutes":1259},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F05\u002Fjavascript-generator-functions\u002F","What Are JavaScript Generator Functions (function*)? The Function You Can Pause and Resume","2025-12-05 13:40:31",1784087329975]